replies.body:
{{champion:62}} 

Because now that Riot has better tech and coding under the hood, they could do so much more to deliver on his theme and make him more fun both to play as and to play against. Point and click doesn't give opponents enough counterplay, and he straddles the diver and assassin roles in a way that he can't quite succeed as either unless he's fed and has item advantages.

---

{{champion:51}} 

Because trap-minefields under turret are downright horrible to play against.

---

{{champion:420}} 

Because instead of dealing burst damage she should be more of a sustained fighter. I'd rather her ultimate have more range and deal less damage but make her tankier somehow rather than have it stay the way it is right now. Having counterplay doesn't change how anti-fun it is to get 5-man ulted by her when you do screw up that counterplay.

---

Edit: wow nobody mentioned Yasuo yet. I guess that meme is dead and people have just given up.
